NAME

   HidraVFX

SUMMARY

   High dynamic range visual effect library and command line application.

NEWS

   2011.03.19 - 0.3.0 released. New features: color space conversions, fractal
                set generation.
   2011.03.15 - HidraVFX 0.2.0 released. New features: basic analytic textures
                added.
   2011.03.07 - First version of HidraVFX 0.1.0 released.

DESCRIPTION

   Features:
    * Image blendings.
    * Distorsion effects.
    * Texture generations.
    * Fractal generations.
    * Channel manipulations and color space conversions
    * Processing HDR/floating point images. Supported format: PFM - Portable
      Float Map.
    * Position dependent parameters. Parameter fields can be specified with
      images instead of single values.
    * Anti-alias for effect where applicable.
    * CLI interface with Bash parameter completion support.

INSTALL

   cmake .
   make
   make install

LICENSE

   GPLv3

